</span></p></dd><dt><a class='title-link' name='host_password' href='#host_password'></a> host_password</dt><dd><p class='desc'><span class='type'>(<span class='string'>string</span>)</span><span class='required'>(Optional)</span><span class='description'><p>Your Local Smappee password.</p>
</span></p></dd><dt><a class='title-link' name='client_id' href='#client_id'></a> client_id</dt><dd><p class='desc'><span class='type'>(<span class='string'>string</span>)</span><span class='required'>(Optional)</span><span class='description'><p>Your Smappee API client ID.</p>
